*[[Bryan Mantia]] – drums, percussion
*[[Richard Fortus]] – rhythm guitar, backing vocals
*[[Bumblefoot (musician)|Bumblefoot]] – lead guitar
*[[Frank Ferrer]] – drums, percussion

