Note: Rose has confirmed some of Buckethead parts will remain on ''Chinese Democracy''<ref name="Axl responds to Dr Pepper">{{cite web|url = http://www.gunsnroses.com/news/article.jsp?ymd=20080326&content_id=a1&vkey=news&fext=.jsp|title = Press Release From Axl Regarding Dr Pepper|accessdate = 2008-03-27 |author=Rose, Axl |date=  2008-03-26|publisher = GunsNRoses.com}}</ref>

